FINISH-0010
When the podcast completes, control will return to the main menu.
FINISH-0020
Pressing the back kill terminates the play of the audio currently in progress and treats this the same as playing the podcast to the end.  That is, if it is selected again, play starts at the beginning.
FINISH-0030
When the podcast completes, the play menu will become dormant and pressing the back key will present the play list.
